{
  "stem": "12904.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the time when her brother, Gunter, my cousin, first cousin, whom I saw in '89, was in the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was accepted because he was blonde and blue-eyed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his mother was-- this was the mother of my cousin Edith-- was hidden in the basement of their home so she would not be deported.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was scheduled to be deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had her orders.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had told me that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First time I went back in 1967, my aunt-- Irma was her name-- told me that she had had her deportation orders.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But her husband, who was faithful to her, protected her-- even though we didn't like the fact that he had Hitler pictures up in his house before we left already-- but he did that in order to protect her, his wife.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when he had meetings for his colleagues in his house, they thought, you know, it's a nice house with Hitler pictures.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the daughter, as I said, we were very close at one time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had vacations together, my sister and my cousin and I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would go with them or she would go with us or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So but she-- in later years, they did not differentiate anymore, and I knew that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know how her brother, Gunter-- the one I saw in '89-- because he won't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wouldn't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I don't know how he was spared from being deported, as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was haunted--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All her life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in '86 finally succeeded in committing suicide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think she'd had that on her mind for a long time because-- although her mother was dead by then.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
